				<h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-light text-emerald-900 mb-6">Tech Stack Details</h2>
				
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Framework</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700">Built with <strong>Astro</strong>, a modern static site generator that delivers lightning-fast performance with minimal JavaScript.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Styling</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700"><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> provides utility-first styling with custom color schemes (emerald, amber, stone) and glassmorphism effects.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Animation & Interaction</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700"><strong>GSAP (GreenSock)</strong> powers smooth animations including the hero title reveal, background carousel transitions, and scroll-triggered parallax effects.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Smooth Scrolling</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700"><strong>Lenis</strong> provides buttery-smooth scrolling with momentum and easing for an elegant browsing experience.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Splash Screen</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700"><strong>LottieFiles</strong> delivers the animated wedding rings loading screen with lightweight, vector-based animations.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Form Backend</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700">RSVP submissions handled via <strong>Formspree</strong>, a powerful form backend that handles all submissions, validation, and email notifications without requiring server-side code.</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Hosting & Deployment</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-700">Deployed on <strong>Netlify</strong> for optimal performance and automatic deployments.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Features -->
